name: I C Faces Design Mens Cotton Tshirt
description:
A premium quality 180gsm ring spun cotton T-shirt, sourced from only responsible suppliers. All finely skiled screened with original artwork. Careful consideration has been given to colour choice and detail, including a custom 3D printed emblem. 

Every product we dispatch will come with a recycled card gift bag, gloss print of the design,sticker pack and an earth friendly cotton eco tote bag.

With a generous fit for the oversized look. 

• Taped rib neck. Sizes S to XXL
• Plain sleeve hem.
• Side seams.
• Twin needle stitching at neck, hem and
sleeves.

XS S M L XL XXL 3XL
Chest - to fit inches 34-36 36-38 38-40 40-44 44-46 48 50-52
